<div class="container">
  <% workout_preferences = WorkoutPreference.where(user_id: current_user.id) %>

  <% if workout_preferences.any? %>
    <strong>Hello, <%= current_user.name %>!</strong><br>
    <p>We're excited to be part of your fitness journey. Below, you'll find a list of your workout plans:</p>
    <hr>
      <% workout_preferences.reverse_each.with_index do |workout_preference, index| %>
      <div class="row">
      <div class="col-12 col-md-4 order-md-2 bg-secondary">
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Fitness Goal:</strong> <%= workout_preference.fitness_goal %></li>
        <li><strong>Days per Week:</strong> <%= workout_preference.days_per_week %></li>
        <li><strong>Time per Session:</strong> <%= workout_preference.time_per_session %> minutes</li>
        <li><strong>Fitness Level:</strong> <%= workout_preference.fitness_level %></li>
        <li><strong>Additional Comments:</strong> <%= workout_preference.additional_comments %></li>
      </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col-6 col-md-8 order-md-1 bg-info">
      <pre>
      <p>Week <%= workout_preferences.length - index %></p>
        <%=workout_preference.workout_plan%>
      </pre>
      </div>
      </div>
      <br>
    <% end %>
  <% else %>
       <p>It looks like you haven't generated any workout plans yet. Don't worry; we're here to help you get started on your fitness journey.</p>
    <p>Benefits of having a personalized workout plan:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Customized workouts tailored to your fitness goals.</li>
      <li>Efficient use of your time with the right exercises and sessions.</li>
      <li>Progress tracking to help you stay motivated and see results.</li>
      <li>Expert guidance based on your fitness level and preferences.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Click <a href="<%= new_user_workout_preference_path(current_user) %>">here</a> to generate your first workout plan and unlock these benefits.</p>

  <% end %>
</div>
